                            <comment id="27024" author="juergen.hoeller" created="Sun, 21 Oct 2007 22:35:41 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;We previously didn&apos;t officially support the use of Spring&apos;s JSP form tag library with FreeMarker. We do support it as of Spring 2.5, and also addressed this issue for 2.5 already. (The root cause is some rather unexpected JspWriter handling in FreeMarker.)&lt;/p&gt;

